org.skife.jdbi.v2.sqlobject

Annotation Type BindMap


  • @Retention(value=RUNTIME)
 @Target(value=PARAMETER)
public @interface BindMap
    Bind a Map<String, Object>

    • Optional Element Summary

      Optional Elements 
      Modifier and Type Optional Element and Description
      boolean implicitKeyStringConversion
      Specify key handling.
      String prefix
      If specified, key key will be bound as prefix.key.
      String[] value
      The list of allowed map keys to bind.

    • Element Detail

      • implicitKeyStringConversion

        public abstract boolean implicitKeyStringConversion
        Specify key handling. If false, Map keys must be strings, or an exception is thrown. If true, any object may be the key, and it will be converted with Object.toString().
        Default:
        false

      • prefix

        public abstract String prefix
        If specified, key key will be bound as prefix.key.
        Default:
        "___jdbi_bare___"

      • value

        public abstract String[] value
        The list of allowed map keys to bind. If not specified, to binds all provided Map entries. Any missing parameters will cause an exception. If specified, binds all provided keys. Missing entries are bound with a SQL NULL.
        Default:
        {}
